data.snippet:
Our poster focuses on self-care and why its important for community health workers (or other direct professionals) to prioritize their own self-care. We also provide number of ways to establish a self-care routine as well as various resources for self-care needs. Next steps in this project include providing extra resources to assist Community Health workers in their duties, clear language toolkits on tackling some challenging conversations with individuals and their families.

Authors: Andrea Witwer PhD, Manisha Khatiwada, Durga Subedi, Durga Mishra

data.title: Introducing the Coalition Network - General Catalyst
data.snippet:
The Future of Services

  Portfolio

Famiglia

#### GC Wealth

An independent full-service wealth management firm to serve transformational individuals, families, and organizations.

#### Catalyst Advisors

Successful and tenured builders are part of our Famiglia and committed to scaling up the next generation of leaders.

#### The Famiglia Effect

Our Famiglia is a place where leading CEOs, founders, partners, and policymakers come together to shape the future.

Transformation

#### Percepta

Transforming critical institutions using applied AI

#### Health Assurance Transformation Company

Our platform for transforming proactive, accessible healthcare.

#### General Catalyst Institute

Helping the entrepreneurial ecosystem partners with governments worldwide. [...] GC is a founding partner of the Coalition Network.

The elegant model is a win-win-win for everyone involved. GC’s founders get access to talented and diverse advisors without taking additional dilution or slowing their fundraising process. Top operators get access to advisory opportunities with vetted startups where they can build their track records and connect with a community of peers at a similar inflection point in their careers. GC gets to support our founders, expand our network and extend access beyond the people we already know. We have some real skin in the game, sharing a portion of our financial upside with the operators in the Coalition Network. By standardizing on this model, we can deliver an incredible experience to each individual company, with portfolio-scale impact. [...] The Coalition Network was built to diversify the cap tables of some of the world’s most promising start-ups by creating a community of prominent women and women of color who are eager to leverage their talents and expertise as founders, operators and angel investors.  The Coalition Network is the brainchild of four powerhouse women - Toyin Ajayi co-founder of Cityblock Health, Lindsay Ullman co-founder of Umbrella, Jackie Nelson co-founder of Tribe AI, and Ashley Mayer former VP of Communications at Glossier–who together understand the tremendous benefit this untapped talent pool can offer to founders and their companies. When the team first ran the idea by me in 2020, I knew it was something my partners and I had to help bring to life.

GC is a founding partner of the Coalition Network.

# Salary Database

The compensation data search results include all non-student employees’ base salary as of 12/31/24. This database is updated yearly in the spring.

## About the Data

Base Pay –Employee's base salary (unclassified staff) or hourly wage (classified staff) as of 12/31/24.

Entries with a zero salary represents Adjunct or Early Retiree Faculty. Adjuncts and Early Retiree Faculty are paid by the semester through our Individual Compensation Distribution System (ICD).
